body.description: For a quick and convenient commute, stash everything in this Kenneth Cole Reaction pebbled vegan leather single compartment 15” laptop and tablet messenger shoulder bag. Made with a leather-like pebbled faux leather exterior with tear-resistant, fully lined polyester interior, this bag is perfect for everyday use. Its single compartment, slim, flapover construction with dual magnetic snap closure has plenty of space to store your items, including a laptop or tablet with a 15-inch screen. Interior also includes a padded tablet pocket. Additionally, this messenger bag features a rear exterior, full-length open top pocket with a magnetic snap closure that provides more easy-access storage space for items that you need readily on-hand. Shoulder bag features a permanent, adjustable shoulder strap extends 60 inches for ease of carrying. ★ Backed by a manufacturer lifetime limited guarantee against defects. ★ Overall Size: 16.5” L x 10” H x 2.5” D. ★ Laptop Dimensions: 15.5” L x 9.75” H x 0.5” D. ★ Product Weight: 1.6 lbs. ★ A simple, yet stylish bag for work, school, or travel. ★

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Kenneth Cole Kenneth Cole started his business in September of 1982 selling shoes out of a 40-foot trailer in Midtown Manhattan. Today, the company is a fashion leader and has taken an edgy approach to many categories including business and travel with their Kenneth Cole Reaction line. For over 30 years, Kenneth Cole has embraced the essence of New York – its boldness, its energy, and its diversity. New Yorkers are born in every city, in every country, every day, because being a New Yorker is a courageous state of mind.

Kenneth Cole Brand Kenneth Cole Reaction appeals to fashion-conscious consumers who value both style and function. Each piece reflects a casual urban perspective and a lifestyle uniquely associated with Kenneth Cole. Kenneth Cole Reaction bags feature bold colors, clean lines, and high-quality materials – all of which add up to a casual, yet modern style perfect for both men and women. Kenneth Cole vouches for its uncompromised dedication to providing its customers with a variety of fashion-forward high-quality products with superior workmanship. Whether you are heading to the office or to the airport, when you venture out and travel with a bag from Kenneth Cole, we want you to embark on your journey with confidence and peace of mind. This is why we are keen to even the smallest of details while putting emphasis on fashion, functionality, quality, and durability above all else. Life has a way of coming at us all quickly, so it’s best to be ready for anything, anywhere.

Kenneth Cole Reaction Flapover Laptop Messenger Bag By Kenneth Cole Reaction Cruising to the office or tearing through the terminal, “The Grand Tour” 15” laptop messenger bag from designer Kenneth Cole is the answer to your business and travel commuting needs. Made with a leather-like pebbled PU exterior that is easy to wipe clean, the bag also features a fully lined interior to help keep your belongings protected. The messenger bag fits most laptops or tablets with up to a 15-inch screen, making it perfect for any business travel. The main compartment features a padded tablet pocket, two gusseted open top pockets, and two pen loops, leaving plenty of room to store other essentials. The single compartment flapover features dual magnetic snap closures, helping to keep belongings safely inside. The rear exterior also provides storage space, with a full length open top pocket with a magnetic snap closure. Its permanent, adjustable shoulder strap also makes for comfortable carrying to and from your destination. Dimensions Overall Size: 16.5” L x 10.0” H x 2.5” D. Weight: 1.6 lbs. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, weightless and better than expected
reviews.reviewText: I've been looking for a cross body bag big enough to carry my laptop and tons of stuff. Have had a lot of bad purchases (gifted to family members), but this covered most of the bases. Wish it were just an inch or two longer, but all in all, study construction, enough places to put things in and the most surprising feature is even with all my crap in it, it still is relatively weightless. Not sure how that happened, but it was a nice surprise. Seems well constructed and if I had any complaint it would be, I'd like to see a little thicker material used. But then it wouldn't be as weightless right?

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 8, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars TABLET bag only!
reviews.reviewText: While I like the quality of the bag, and I love the look, I cannot give it a good rating because of the misrepresentation of its size. The overall size measurements are not correct, and the “laptop” pocket size is far too small for a laptop. I have a 14 inch laptop (which is small enough to fit in a 13 inch laptop sleeve) but it does not come anywhere close to fitting into the pocket in this bag. I’m not even sure my iPad in its case would fit in it. Also, the bag does not have much, if any, padding.Because I like the bag, I decided to purchase a protective sleeve, and it now fits perfectly in the main compartment of this bag and is protected. I’m disappointed to have to spend extra money for the protection that I thought this bag would provide, but cest la vie. Yes, I might return it. But, it will make a fine purse if I don’t.I included a photo of the inside of the tag so that you can see the actual measurements, and that the brand designed it for tablets.
